CloudFormation error: !Base64 cannot have null value @ example-templates/errors/cloudformation-null-value.yaml:11:25 (errno: IY7001)
  -> invalid CloudFormation intrinsic function

  10 |     Properties:
  11 |       UserData: !Base64 null  # Invalid - cannot have null value
     |                         ^^^^ invalid CloudFormation tag

   !Base64 expects a non-null string value
   example: UserData: !Base64 'echo Hello'
   example: Script: !Base64 !Sub 'echo ${Parameter}'

   For more info: iidy explain IY7001
